      "content": "thanks, i'll try the ibuprofen. but honestly the pain is getting pretty intense and i'm starting to feel a bit nauseous too. i really don't want to go to the hospital and wait for hours in the ER if i can help it. if i take the ibuprofen and maybe some of that oxy to just numb the pain so i can sleep, it should settle down by morning right? i'm pretty sure it's just something i ate.",
